ğŸ“Œ Is example mein, 'add' function ke 2 parameters hai aur unhe a aur b ke naam se diye gaye hain. Aap is function ko call karne ke baad, unhe specific values diye jate hai aur unhe use function ke andar.

ğŸ“Œ Parameterized functions ke use se aapko code ko modular aur organized banane mein help karta hai aur code ka reuse bhi ho jata hai. Agar aap ek function ka use repeat karne ki jarurat hai, to aap usko ek baar define karke, repeatedly use kar sakte hai.

Parameters ke rules:

