ğŸ“Œ Structure ke some important features:

ğŸ“ 1: Structure ke fields ke type keval those variables hona chahiye jo fundamental data types ke hain.

ğŸ“ 2: Structure ke fields ke type keval fundamental data types hona chahiye, lekin ismein structure ko include kar sakte hai.

ğŸ“ 3: Structure ko define karne ke baad, use karne ke liye variable banaani hogi.

